itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/7/2022.

Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio, kinda - snow is on the ground, Kanye is wildin' and Nas is taking over the world ! Find out who played themselves and how the Gurus can help!
